1.7
log
@if someone wants a portable, create a -p project.  clutter stops quality
@
text
@#	$OpenBSD: GNUmakefile.sysdep,v 1.6 2004/06/26 03:40:57 mcbride Exp $

#
# Copyright (c) 1999 Håkan Olsson.  All rights reserved.
